<div class="page-header"><h1>About Pinnacle Sales</h1><p>23+ years connecting Western US dealers with premium cabinetry brands.</p></div>
<div class="content-narrow section">
<Breadcrumbs items={[{name:'Home',href:'/'},{name:'About'}]} />

<p>Pinnacle Sales is the leading manufacturers' representative firm serving independent kitchen and bath dealers across the Western United States. For over two decades, we have built our reputation on one core belief: when dealers succeed, everyone wins — manufacturers, homeowners, and the industry as a whole.</p>

<p>We represent five premium cabinetry brands — <a href="/brands/shiloh-cabinetry">Shiloh Cabinetry</a>, <a href="/brands/eclipse-cabinetry">Eclipse Cabinetry</a>, <a href="/brands/aspect-cabinetry">Aspect Cabinetry</a>, <a href="/brands/pronorm-german-kitchens">Pronorm German Kitchens</a>, and <a href="/brands/vistora-closets">Vistora Closets</a> — giving our dealer partners access to the full spectrum of kitchen and bath solutions, from value-driven semi-custom to ultra-premium European design.</p>

<h2>Our Mission: Connect | Collaborate | Create</h2>

<p><strong>Connect</strong> dealers with the right brands for their market and clientele. <strong>Collaborate</strong> with showroom teams through hands-on training, design services, and business development support. <strong>Create</strong> lasting partnerships built on trust, product knowledge, and a shared commitment to helping homeowners build beautiful spaces.</p>

<p>We exist to help independent kitchen dealers grow profitable businesses. That means more than just placing orders — it means working alongside your team to close projects, train staff on new product lines, plan showroom displays that sell, and develop marketing strategies that bring qualified traffic through your door.</p>

<h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>

<p>Our team is always training — making sure they are up to date with industry standards and product innovations. With members from diverse backgrounds and experiences, we think through projects from every angle and help address issues before they happen, keeping your business running smoothly.</p>

<p>Pinnacle Sales is intentional about the manufacturers we represent. We foster long-term, meaningful relationships with both vendors and clients. This selectivity ensures that every brand in our portfolio meets the quality, support, and value standards our dealers expect.</p>

<p>Continual growth opportunities help our team foster a culture of entrepreneurial cooperation — focused on setting standards in the marketplace for client retention and satisfaction. Our commitment to integrity ensures that when we succeed, we do so ethically and responsibly across the board.</p>

