<h2>Our Territory</h2>

<p>We serve kitchen and bath dealers in 10 Western states: <a href="/territory/arizona">Arizona</a>, <a href="/territory/california">California</a>, <a href="/territory/colorado">Colorado</a>, <a href="/territory/idaho">Idaho</a>, <a href="/territory/montana">Montana</a>, <a href="/territory/nevada">Nevada</a>, <a href="/territory/new-mexico">New Mexico</a>, <a href="/territory/oregon">Oregon</a>, <a href="/territory/utah">Utah</a>, and <a href="/territory/washington">Washington</a>.</p>

<p>Our WW Wood Products brands (Shiloh, Eclipse, and Aspect) are available across all 10 states. <a href="/brands/pronorm-german-kitchens">Pronorm German Kitchens</a> are available nationwide with protected dealer territories. <a href="/brands/vistora-closets">Vistora Closets</a> are available throughout our Western US footprint.</p>

<h2>Our Manufacturer Partners</h2>

<p><strong>WW Wood Products</strong> — Based in Missouri, WW Wood is one of America's premier semi-custom and custom cabinetry manufacturers. They produce Shiloh Cabinetry, Eclipse Cabinetry, and Aspect Cabinetry with industry-leading customization options, competitive lead times, and a commitment to American craftsmanship. Pinnacle Sales is the exclusive WW Wood dealer representative across our Western US territory.</p>

<p><strong>Pronorm Einbauküchen</strong> — A leading German fitted kitchen manufacturer based in Vlotho, Germany. Pronorm combines precision engineering, sustainable manufacturing, and contemporary European design to produce some of the finest kitchens in the world. European Kitchen Distributors (EKD), led by Pinnacle Sales, is the exclusive US agent for Pronorm.</p>

<p><strong>Vistora</strong> — A made-to-order closet and storage solutions manufacturer offering a wide range of finishes, configurations, and organizational accessories. Vistora brings the same commitment to quality and customization that our dealers expect across all product categories.</p>

<h2>Industry Certifications</h2>

<p>Pinnacle Sales is a certified member of the <strong>National Kitchen & Bath Association (NKBA)</strong>, the industry's leading professional organization for kitchen and bath specialists. Our NKBA certification reflects our commitment to ongoing professional development, industry best practices, and ethical standards in dealer representation.</p>

